{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 1''' is the 1st day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * [[敏達天皇]] 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[585]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In response to an appeal by the anti-Buddhist advocate {{ill|Mononobe no Moriya|ja|物部守屋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, who claimed that the spread of Buddhism was the cause of an epidemic, the court reported this to the emperor. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1587]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} set out with 25,000 troops to subjugate the Shimazu clan in Kyushu. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadakuni|ja|水野忠邦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} assumed the office of {{ill|Rōjū|ja|老中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, implementing the Tenpō reforms. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill