== Events == * [[:ja:敏達天皇|敏達天皇]] 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[585]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – In response to an appeal by the anti-Buddhist advocate {{ill|Mononobe no Moriya|ja|物部守屋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, who claimed that the spread of Buddhism was the cause of an epidemic, the court reported this to the emperor. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1587]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} set out with 25,000 troops to subjugate the Shimazu clan in Kyushu. * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Mizuno Tadakuni|ja|水野忠邦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} assumed the office of {{ill|Rōjū|ja|老中|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, implementing the Tenpō reforms. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – Post offices (now known as {{ill|Yūbin-kyoku|ja|郵便局|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) were established in Tokyo, Kyoto, and Osaka, marking the beginning of postal services (recognized as Postal Memorial Day).
== Births == * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1829]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Inoue Genzaburō|ja|井上源三郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a member of the Shinsengumi (died [[1868]]). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1864]] {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Wakamatsu Sentako|ja|若松賎子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a translator (died [[1896]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Mutō Yamaichi|ja|武藤山治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a businessperson and manager of the Kanebo conglomerate (died [[1934]]). * Meiji 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimura Gentarō|ja|志村源太郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a banker and president of the Nippon Kangyo Bank (died [[1930]]).
== Deaths == * [[:ja:欽明天皇|欽明天皇]] 32nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[570]] {{ill|March 22|ja|3月22日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Soga Iname|ja|蘇我稲目|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a great minister (died ?; birth year may be around [[506]]). * [[:ja:弘仁|弘仁]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[817]] {{ill|March 21|ja|3月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Katsumichi|ja|勝道|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the founder of Nikko-san (born [[735]]).
