== Births == * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1829]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Inoue Genzaburō|ja|井上源三郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inoue Genzaburō|qq=}}, a member of the Shinsengumi (died [[1868]]). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genji|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1864]] {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 6|qq=}}) – {{ill|Wakamatsu Sentako|ja|若松賎子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamatsu Sentako|qq=}}, a translator (died [[1896]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mutō Yamaichi|ja|武藤山治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutō Yamaichi|qq=}}, a businessperson and manager of the Kanebo conglomerate (died [[1934]]). * Meiji 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1867]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shimura Gentarō|ja|志村源太郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimura Gentarō|qq=}}, a banker and president of the Nippon Kangyo Bank (died [[1930]]).
